    <p>Another issue cited is the inconsistent billing practices. Some homeowners noted being quoted one amount, then invoiced a higher total. In a competitive market like Fort Worth, trust and clarity are critical—and unfortunately, this company has developed a track record for missing the mark in those areas.</p>

