    <p>Michael has responded to some complaints online but rarely posts updates or clarifies policies. Yelp reviewers have mentioned being ghosted after deposits were paid. While a few locals support Burdman for small jobs, others recommend looking for electricians with dedicated staff and office support.</p>

    <p>Before hiring Burdman Electric, be sure to request a detailed written estimate and timeline. Ask if Michael will be the one performing the work or if it will be a subcontractor. Confirm the project scope, pricing, and payment schedule. Don’t assume anything—document everything.</p>

